## Limitations

This report is based on available data and articles up to October 2023. The findings are subject to change as new data emerges. Additionally, the perspectives provided are primarily from U.S.-based sources, which may not fully capture global labor market trends. The lack of specific data on certain demographic groups may also limit the comprehensiveness of the analysis.